{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c09b7dae-7f72-454b-af6b-d2fe5981972e",
    "name": "Auth App - IAM Server",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Auth_App IAM Server.\n\nBase URL: [http://localhost:8080/api](http://localhost:8080/api)\n\n── SETUP ──────────────────────────────────\n\n1. Import this collection.\n    \n2. Set `baseUrl` collection variable (default: [http://localhost:8080/api](http://localhost:8080/api)).\n    \n3. Hit any GET endpoint first (e.g. OIDC Discovery) — Spring will plant the XSRF-TOKEN cookie.\n    \n4. The collection pre-request script reads that cookie and auto-populates {{xsrfToken}}.\n    \n5. All state-changing /admin/** requests automatically send X-XSRF-TOKEN.\n    \n\n── CSRF RULES (from SecurityConfig) ──────  \nIgnored (no CSRF needed):  \n/auth/login, /auth/register, /auth/refresh,  \n/auth/logout/single, /auth/logout/all, /auth/certs,  \n/onboard,  \n/{realm}/protocol/openid-connect/token  \n/{realm}/protocol/openid-connect/register  \n/{realm}/protocol/openid-connect/token/introspect  \n/{realm}/protocol/openid-connect/userinfo\n\nProtected (X-XSRF-TOKEN required):  \nAll POST / PUT / DELETE under /admin/**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "42335900"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.jwtToken)     pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken',  res.jwtToken);",
                  "if (res.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                  "console.log('Tokens saved to collection variables.');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@yourapp.com\",\n  \"password\": \"ChangeMe123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
